Required Libraries list :

For your Voice-Based Bill Generator project in Python, you'll typically need the following libraries. Here's a list of them along with the pip install commands:

Library Name | Purpose | Install Command

speechrecognition | To convert voice input into text | pip install SpeechRecognition

pyaudio | To access the microphone for voice input | pip install pyaudio

pyttsx3 | For text-to-speech output (speaking out the bill, etc.) | pip install pyttsx3

tabulate | To display tabular data in the terminal | pip install tabulate

simply just run these commonds in your terminal :
pip install SpeechRecognition
pip install pyaudio
pip install pyttsx3
pip install tabulate
